OL,3,CMurder investigation after 88-year-old
OL,4,Cwoman dies in care home
OL,6,FLincolnshire police have commenced a
OL,7,Fmurder investigation after an elderly
OL,8,Fwoman was found dead in a care home in
OL,9,FSleaford.
OL,11,FOfficers were called to Sleaford Manor
OL,12,FCare Home in Sandringham Way, around
OL,13,F2am on Sunday 22 March, to reports an
OL,14,F88-year-old woman had died.
OL,16,FTwo people, age 74 and 75, were
OL,17,Farrested in connection with the
OL,18,Fincident and have since been released
OL,19,Ffrom custody.
