OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1774361471
OL,3,CMurder investigation after 88-year-old
OL,4,Cwoman dies in care home
OL,6,FFollowing a postmortem examination,
OL,7,Fpolice have now confirmed the death is
OL,8,Fbeing treated as suspected murder.
OL,10,FDetective Inspector Mel Rooke, of the
OL,11,FMajor Crime Unit, said: "Our thoughts
OL,12,Fare with the family and friends of the
OL,13,Fvictim this evening. Our specially
OL,14,Ftrained officers will be providing
OL,15,Fsupport to her family as our inquiry
OL,16,Fcontinues.
OL,26,@sD@YOU
