CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1774361471
OL,3,CMurder investigation after 88-year-old
OL,4,Cwoman dies in care home
OL,6,F"I understand any unexpected death is
OL,7,Fa concern to our communities and this
OL,8,Ftragic death will be no different. I
OL,9,Fcan say there is no wider risk to the
OL,10,Fpublic. Our inquiries will take some
OL,11,Ftime to complete and I would ask that
OL,12,Fthe family and the care home are left
OL,13,Fin peace and their privacy is
OL,14,Frespected."
OL,16,FSleaford Manor Care Home is ran by
OL,17,FCare UK.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@KO]
