OL,3,CMurder investigation after 88-year-old
OL,4,Cwoman dies in care home
OL,6,FA Care UK spokesperson said: "We are
OL,7,Fdeeply saddened by this incident and
OL,8,Fsend our condolences to the resident's
OL,9,Ffamily.
OL,11,FThey added: "We will be cooperating
OL,12,Fwith the investigation in any way we
OL,13,Fcan."
